Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  小優
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.18,title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}「難道是試膽大會！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.18,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,750)}「難道是試膽大會！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到小楓的郵件說是大家來放煙花的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她自己卻不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  琴音沒和你在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她早我兩個小時出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像帶了很多東西的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來那個包裹裡好像有長髮的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,長髮是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  這是小楓的留言？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  是不是發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就分成兩組去找琴音和小楓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  抽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是試膽大會！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,試膽大會啊  好久沒玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  好可怕啊春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在一起就不會有事的  小優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吻…吻我一下或許就不會害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  我也是黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  春香那是橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  怎麼看都是黃色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.41,0:14:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思  我不能和小優在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要相同顏色的組一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶  我是黃色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小雫  我們一組了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這反應是什麼情況啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  我是隊友你不滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小柚感覺完全不會害怕的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事故感不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好可怕～～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  沒有感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是優還真是對不住了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小優  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優她離我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  我們一起吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小柚～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是進行了交換
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那春香你們10分鐘後跟來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還來得及回頭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在耍我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香你也只有現在能說說風涼話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真要有什麼情況我可不救你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  我隨口說說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十分鐘後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尾隨而來的美月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優這孩子  居然這麼晚還到這種地方來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  果然和春香同學在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還好平時在頭飾上塗了螢光塗料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來這地方還真讓人不怎麼舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能害怕  想點什麼開心的事再尾隨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開心的事…  開心的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長  張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能是春香同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會想起春香同學啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…春香  剛剛有沒有看到什麼東西在閃光？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是我的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出現啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊  小優
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別把我扔下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.19,0:17:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  一下子就傳出了悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是…看到了什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟過來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優  你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什麼東西跟過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  要是跟到這裡來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吻…吻我一下或許就不會害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定真會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  小優…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  吻我一下或許就不會害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被看穿了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  居然這麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說怪物也是小楓或者琴音的其中一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  春香…快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心中有什麼東西覺醒了的春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我平靜下來以前  請一直吻著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停不下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我一定要讓你平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優  你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優？優  你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在叫我的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,優！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  優
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月會長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是跟在你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們為什麼會抱在一起啊  給我分開！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之姐姐  趕緊從這裡出去比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛才就在被人喊著名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別嚇唬你姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是春香同學一邊喊著優的名字一邊在接吻嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:19:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有喊名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你整天就這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別走散了  一起行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.49,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,注：投懷送抱之後的左擁右抱之姐妹丼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必了  我就一個人回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟春香同學靠那麼近  我的心臟受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕就害怕了  不用不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三個人在一起就不會害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是這麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就當作是這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,再注：順理成章之姐妹丼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  優  好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,試膽大會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒說是試膽大會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說了來放煙花的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還搞抽籤什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  似乎多了個不該存在的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本來是想搞試膽大會的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只準備了煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,試膽大會明年再弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好不容易做了些簽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得不抽太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那跟在我後面叫我名字的是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼  別說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就只做了煙花的準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小優  冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.33,0:22:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同學真是個體貼的人呢
