Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我更喜歡炒麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然炒麵我也很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.28,0:23:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.31,0:23:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是在海邊小店吃的炒麵最棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我更喜歡杯麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.19,0:23:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦！
