Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「和姐姐一起喝茶吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和「魔女與蘋果與姐姐」這兩篇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.57,0:24:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
